cat << EOF
Digikam now uses a plugin architecture for additional functionality.
Currently implemented plugins are:

1) RawConverter: A Raw Image Converter for digital cameras
2) SlideShow   : Slideshow with effects ripped out from kslideshow
3) MpegEncoder : An images to MPEG encoder for build a video file with many images.
4) HTMLExport  : An Album to HTML gallery export.

An 'HelloWorld' plugin exist for explain the plugin implementation with the Digikam
interface.
EOF
